<h1 id="why-virtual-reality">Why virtual reality?</h1>
<p>I think the brain is incredible. Not just the human brain, but any brain really. An organ dedicated to processing information, enabling animals to sense, move and adapt. How did they evolve? <em>Why</em> did they evolve?</p>

<p>Why am I saying this? Well, because I am a neuroscientist at heart, this is a neuroscientific project, and virtual reality only becomes valuable seen in this light.</p>

